    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>记住以下守则：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259310/extras/f4dec5e3cc054a53f69222cdb4c0d6eb.poster.avif?t=1749494748\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259310/extras/f4dec5e3cc054a53f69222cdb4c0d6eb.webm?t=1749494748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259310/extras/f4dec5e3cc054a53f69222cdb4c0d6eb.mp4?t=1749494748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 猫是好的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 猫主子不高兴时，请立刻返回。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 不要向猫主子询问仓库历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. 收到订单时，需熟记货架信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. 所有的订单和货物都没有出错。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. 这是间无人仓库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7. 听见货箱自行移动的声音，迅速离开现场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8. 独自完成所有订单，不要和其他人接触。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259310/extras/ce57f9b91402323c2c96e16c3d06444c.poster.avif?t=1749494748\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259310/extras/ce57f9b91402323c2c96e16c3d06444c.webm?t=1749494748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259310/extras/ce57f9b91402323c2c96e16c3d06444c.mp4?t=1749494748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发货模拟器：</strong>取货、打包、发货，在紧迫的配额压力下完成工作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理恐怖：</strong>探索仓库，每一步都危机重重。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特体验：</strong>每次死亡都会让你进入一个新的仓库，各种动态事件会带来意想不到的挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>揭开谜团：</strong>解锁并探索新区域，逐步拼凑隐藏其中的黑暗真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>生存与陪伴：</strong>保护和照顾你的猫咪，它是你唯一的慰藉和情感寄托。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>工具升级：</strong>将收入再投资来提高效率和生存机会。</p></li></ul>",
